<item>
            <title>[LU-8285] Autotest local.sh incorrectly turns off LNet logging</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8285</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The autotest config file local.sh turns off three subsystems by default: LNet, LNDs, and pinger.  This could be hiding critical network-related logs during autotest runs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This ticket is for changing local.sh so these three subsystems are on by default.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
